FluxTE - Flux Template Engine
A lightweight and logical template engine.

Features & Concepts:
- Lightweight
- Logical
- Easy to use and implement
- Scalable

Instruction tokens:
- # = If
- ! = Else
- / = EndIf
- & = Include
- $ = Var

Usage:
{(token)variable_name}
- Ex. {&view} for include of the filepath inside the view variable.
- Ex. {$view} to display the variable.